data.title: Caglar Birinci
data.meta_description: Caglar Birinci - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Caglar Birinci is a Turkish civil engineer with over 14 years of experience in underground, metro, railway, and marine structure design and construction. He has worked on various projects in Turkey, Europe, the Middle East, Africa, and Scandinavia. Currently he works as a senior civil engineer in Gothenburg, Sweden providing technical support for railway projects. He holds a bachelor's degree in civil engineering and has intermediate language skills in English, Swedish, and Spanish.
